descript.abstract: A summary list of military owned and leased lands in San Diego County. All major facilities are depicted. Some military owned housing units are not depicted. Data is current as of the update date. All base names are current.
descript.purpose: To indicate where military facilities and owned lands are in San Diego County. This data set is required for state regulatory compliance if certain land use activities are within a given distance of a military facility. Data is subject to change.
descript.supplinf: Data is maintained by Land Use and Environment Group for regulatory purposes. Not all property ownership of military lands aligns with actual controlled space of a military facility. Comments and corrections are welcome.
